        {"concepts": ["BP", "EVT", "recanalization"], "expected_sections": ["4.3"]},
        {"concepts": ["BP", "TICI"], "expected_sections": ["4.3"]}
      ],
      "note": "4.3 has BP recs mentioning EVT and TICI grades. 4.7.4 has failed EVT but no BP targets."
    },
